  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Profitability metrics remain robust despite revenue pressure. Q3 2025 gross margin stood at 46.49%, while operating margin reached 29.99% and net margin came in at 24.92%. These margins demonstrate Apple's pricing power and operational efficiency, with the company converting nearly one-quarter of revenue into net income. The EBITDA margin of 32.82% further underscores strong underlying cash generation capability before non-cash charges.",
